	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000931_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="inline" rend="gray" hand="#hand01">C+C<lb/><hi rend="underline">443</hi></add> <space extent="5" unit="chars"/><date when="1856-12-15">15<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> <choice><abbr>Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>December</expan></choice> 1856</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="12" unit="chars"/><placeName>Mission House</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Friend</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="9" unit="chars"/>Your very 
<lb/>welcome <bibl>note</bibl> of the 
<lb/><date when="1856-12-03">3<hi rend="sup">d</hi></date> I found on my arrival 
<lb/>on Wednesday night &amp; 
<lb/>now thank you for 
<lb/>its contents. We came 
<lb/>from <placeName><settlement type="town">Southampton</settlement></placeName> 
<lb/>on Saturday whither 
<lb/>I had gone to bring 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi> <choice><abbr>L.</abbr><expan>Livingstone</expan></choice></persName> We have several 
<lb/>meetings to attend and 
<lb/>will as soon as possible 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000931_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>go to visit my poor 
<lb/>mother in <placeName><country>Scotland</country></placeName>
<lb/>I shall have very little 
<lb/>time to spend in <placeName><country>England</country></placeName> 
<lb/>as 110 men wait for 
<lb/>me at <placeName><settlement type="town">Tete</settlement></placeName> and I must 
<lb/>get through the <placeName><geogName type="delta"><placeName><settlement type="town">Quilimane</settlement></placeName> 
<lb/>Delta</geogName></placeName> before the unhealthy 
<lb/>season begins. You 
<lb/>have heard of the loss 
<lb/>of my father than 
<lb/>whom there is none 
<lb/>in <placeName><country>England</country></placeName> I should 
<lb/>have liked better to have 
<lb/>narrated my adventures

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000931_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/>I have <choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> no <bibl>letter</bibl> 
<lb/>since one in <date when="1852">1852</date> from 
<lb/><persName>Mary</persName> when <persName>Mamma</persName>
<lb/>whom we all dearly 
<lb/>loved and whose 
<lb/>memory we revere 
<lb/>was not expected to 
<lb/>live. We have no 
<lb/>idea how we shall 
<lb/>be situated but it will 
<lb/>be in some quiet spot 
<lb/>near <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> proper 
<lb/>for <term type="occupation">writing</term>. I shall 
<lb/>not engage in 
<lb/><term type="occupation">speechifying</term>. Present 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_000931_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'-->
<lb/>our kindest regards to 
<lb/>all your family &amp; 
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>believe me ever 
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>Affectionately Yours 
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><persName>David <choice><orig>Livingston</orig><reg>Livingstone</reg></choice></persName></p>
			
